# Never commit raw audit data into the published profile registry.
# Curated audit docs (STOCK-INVENTORY.md, ALIGNMENT-WITH-ZERO.md,
# ARCHITECTURE.md) belong in printers/<id>/docs/ and DO get committed.
# Raw probe dumps + vendor-source clones live one level up at
# installer/.audits/<id>-<date>/ and never enter this repo.
audit/
audits/
.audits/

# Profile-side build artifacts (if a flow ever produces them under a
# printer dir). Profile-yaml-driven artifacts that are part of the
# install (firmware/mcu_klipper.bin, screen-daemon/lib/*.so) ARE
# committed. Generic build cruft is not.
**/build/
**/.cache/
*.deb
*.tar.gz
*.tmp

# Python / yaml linting cruft if any tooling runs locally.
__pycache__/
.mypy_cache/
.pytest_cache/
.venv/
*.pyc
